{
  "stem": "4189.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when I arrived there, I saw a large crowd standing in front of the building there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the fire department was there and the police department was there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And what they did, they were-- the fire department poured water onto the adjacent building because the synagogue was on fire.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they poured that water not on the synagogue to put out the fire, but they put it onto the adjacent building so the adjacent building would not burn.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then as I mingled with the crowd, I found out that the people that are living there, they were all evacuated.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I found out that my aunt was safe, that she was somewhere in the neighborhood with other friends.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went back right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went back to my mother because I didn't want to stay there, because I didn't want to arouse attraction.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was afraid myself, so I peddled back to our home, and I reported to my mother what had happened.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then after that we could not-- of course, the store we couldn't re-open.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to keep the store closed, and there was no store, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was totally destroyed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Nazi regime, on top of all the damages that they did, they imposed a fine on the Jewish population of one billion marks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In other words, they said that we had to pay for the damages that they did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was impossible to stay in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to get out, and the only way to do it now was my mother had a brother that was living in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was not really living there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was a transient because he originally lived in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
